         <div type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><head>Translation</head><p><note>Monogram cross</note> To his good memory. Sambas, son of Stephanus, the guardian of this place, lived in peace for eight years, two months and twenty days. He died on the day of Moon <note>Monday</note> in the month of March in the eighth indiction.</p></div>
